window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When two young girls go missing from a small Georgia town, the crime remains unsolved for nearly 30 years. </p> <p>When Savannah moves home to the small town of Humble, Georgia, she has no intention of getting involved in a kidnapping investigation. But when her older brother Mac becomes the main suspect, Savannah launches a secret investigation in order to clear her brotherâ€™s name. Savannah has inherited a gift, one that might reveal who the culprit is if she can stay one step ahead of the killer, who is closer than she thinks.</p>"; 
